{"name":"article","postlist":[{"title":"從前的脸","slug":"formerface","date":"2014-02-10T15:32:26.000Z","updated":"2020-07-21T13:47:59.416Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/formerface.json","excerpt":"2013.06.16，iphone4S3.5英寸的屏幕里狭窄地框下了我的脸。我拿着刚买两天的它，用新的心情，写了安静。2013.06.23，高考成绩如期而至，六百这样一个完美的整数结束了我并不完美的高中生活。那天，我印象中的都是嘴角弧度向上的脸。现实就是这样，一个好的结局永远好过你自以为艰苦卓绝的奋斗。","keywords":null,"cover":"http://suyan.yezy.tech/cover/formerface.jpg","content":null,"raw":null,"categories":[{"name":"daily","path":"api/categories/daily.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"article","path":"api/tags/article.json"}]},{"title":"安靜","slug":"quiet","date":"2013-06-16T15:32:18.000Z","updated":"2020-07-21T13:47:59.414Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/quiet.json","excerpt":"生活开始变得安静。没有了成堆的试卷让我烦恼，没有了那么多错误需要铭记，没有了颐指气使的人让我明白自己的缺憾。躺在病床上，有时候真的希望过去三年的欢愉和悲伤，能够像那些电镜下令人恶心的东西一样消融在我的身体里，然后我能敢爱、敢恨、敢堂而皇之地直面阳光。","keywords":null,"cover":"http://suyan.yezy.tech/cover/quiet.jpg","content":null,"raw":null,"categories":[{"name":"daily","path":"api/categories/daily.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"article","path":"api/tags/article.json"}]},{"title":"宋崗二路的日子","slug":"thedayinsonggangtworoad","date":"2013-01-04T15:32:10.000Z","updated":"2020-07-21T13:47:59.415Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/thedayinsonggangtworoad.json","excerpt":"直到现在，用了一个接近半个三百六十五天的界限，还是无法确定在高考这根颠簸的钢索上，如何才能抓到成形的勇气。在宋岗二路的日子里，我学会忍受所有飞扬跋扈趾高气扬的鞭策。这个过程中进入眼里的石子，飞进眼里的砂子，勾住裤脚的荆棘，变得深刻。我明白它们带来的痛，带来不容易愈合的伤口。","keywords":null,"cover":"http://suyan.yezy.tech/cover/thedayinsonggangtworoad.jpg","content":null,"raw":null,"categories":[{"name":"daily","path":"api/categories/daily.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"article","path":"api/tags/article.json"}]},{"title":"想，一個人","slug":"missingoneperson","date":"2012-12-21T15:32:00.000Z","updated":"2020-07-21T13:47:59.415Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/missingoneperson.json","excerpt":"十指相扣的瞬间，我让孤独带走所有只关于一个人的想念。镁光灯下，电流刺激的神经，开始将我的记忆放映，徒留下那些人脸上惊愕的表情。","keywords":null,"cover":"http://suyan.yezy.tech/cover/missingoneperson.jpg","content":null,"raw":null,"categories":[{"name":"daily","path":"api/categories/daily.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"article","path":"api/tags/article.json"}]},{"title":"中秋之盼","slug":"theexpectinmidautumn","date":"2012-09-26T15:31:47.000Z","updated":"2020-08-13T15:09:57.853Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/theexpectinmidautumn.json","excerpt":"许一个十八年的期盼苍老在中秋花好月圆之下。一九九四年的那个不安分的秋天，正值中秋节来临之际，上天赐予了那个家庭一种忙前忙后的欢喜。距离中秋节，还剩四天。","keywords":null,"cover":"http://suyan.yezy.tech/cover/theexpectinmidautumn.jpg","content":null,"raw":null,"categories":[{"name":"daily","path":"api/categories/daily.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"article","path":"api/tags/article.json"}]},{"title":"執蘖","slug":"zhinie","date":"2012-06-08T14:40:18.000Z","updated":"2020-07-21T13:47:59.417Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/zhinie.json","excerpt":"蘖，树木被砍去或倒下后长出的新芽。男孩呆呆地盯着电脑屏幕，第二次看着百度百科对这个字所做出的解释。结果可想而知，和第一次的一模一样，但现在的他，已不再是当初那个傻傻坚持的男孩。","keywords":null,"cover":"http://suyan.yezy.tech/cover/zhinie.jpg","content":null,"raw":null,"categories":[{"name":"daily","path":"api/categories/daily.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"article","path":"api/tags/article.json"}]}]}